{"tid":110384,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[最後一次]生日前的最後武士","createTime":"2017-02-06T15:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T16:36:57.000Z","uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d34bbe6d74c296750e110ae8398c4c314bfea1f","tid":110384,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:36:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9FMVmai-I2o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9FMVmai-I2o&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f6bc0d6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9FMVmai-I2o</a><br />\n<br />\nI hurt myself today <br />\nTo see if I still feel <br />\nI focus on the pain <br />\nThe only thing that's real <br />\nThe needle tears a hole<br />\nThe old familiar sting <br />\nTry to kill it all away <br />\nBut I remember everything <br />\n<br />\n本身以為放底左你,但聽到Logan首歌<br />\n回憶又一次過返哂黎<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n      我仲好記得對上一套狼人都係同你睇, 仲好傻好天真咁話要做你既小武士, 係分手之前知道狼人最後一集, 好開心咁同你講, 我地一定要一齊睇! 真係點估到,最後都係去唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n     我地之間既感情維持左大約三時,起起伏伏, 甜酸苦辣, 樣樣齊, 我都同狼人一樣, 因為發生左一D事, 第一次比你飛, 尊嚴同面子通通都唔要, 一心想你返黎我既身邊, 最後真係無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以一齊返,開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n     好可惜我地之間既矛盾其實一直都無去解決, 結果你我心入面既刺都愈來愈多, 愈來愈長, 去到一發不可收執既地步, 最後就直到現在<br />\n    <br />\n     我講過要做你既小武士, 無論係身邊既人點評論你, 我自己遇到既錯折, 無論幾痛 幾辛苦, 我最後都一定會再返黎你身邊, 但最後分手既原因係因為復合後我&quot;無咩進步&quot;, 樣樣野都比唔到你身邊姐妹既男友, 都達唔到你理想既情人, 其實已經分開左大半年, 一切都已經平靜, 但人好奇怪, 總係會無啦啦諗起你, 口講條八婆咪返黎, 個心點諗就係另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n     I will let you down I will make you hurt, 係你眼中 我永遠都只會傷害你, 而唔係愛護你, I cannot repair, 無論你我眼中 我已經修理唔到,返唔到轉頭, I would find a way, 我只可以放手 搵自己條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-----------------------------------------------------<br />\n巴絲打, 無論幾掛住, 付出幾多, 有幾堅定都好, 要完既始終都要完, 有時候一早分開留返少少尊嚴比自己好好活下去, 好過復合 但問題根本解決唔到, 復合後又可以行到幾遠?<br />\n<br />\n不過開心既係, 今年生日 我既願望可以留返比自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望咁多位失戀既朋友友都可以震作!<br />\n<br />\n放手啦 搵個識珍惜你既公主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a90912956aa4849b0888297a1fb22d7963d5f2","tid":110384,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77daa95621d7f3fac23920f59242cd007819aa2e","tid":110384,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:57:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同路人？"},{"pid":"091ac1ba661ec80359c5bcb6109c8f0ae006054f","tid":110384,"uid":3627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:42:05.000Z","msg":"睇到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3992a19defebed81b4ca47bcc0be3dd682a9661c","tid":110384,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:44:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喊完都仰要上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a5bab535e631f3c8cbfefeebde75386d55e41b","tid":110384,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喊完都係要上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b31c3648682851933418e205a1fb1da2795d73c3","tid":110384,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喊完都係要上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5da8fa941591c75dc1fefdc5cb3508041203d8","tid":110384,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4558c7ea4a4fb207ef737bc717c9fa14d120c645","tid":110384,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:46:33.000Z","msg":"加油 生日快樂"},{"pid":"ad5193a4e505a6bb03b6d54f10463bc1fd277988","tid":110384,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油 生日快樂</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf8472668f029a05a9f19e044ff99b35107cdf3","tid":110384,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完套戲<br />\n做人係要忠於自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e9583a3cafaa6a487c7de04a9bafc718bf73ba","tid":110384,"uid":33040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱睇完套戲<br />\n做人係要忠於自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}